summary: Passionate Data Scientist specializing in ML, NLP, and AI, where I focus on driving automation and informed decision-making. With a robust theoretical background and innovative thinking, I am motivated to transform complex data into impactful insights. Adaptability, a collaborative spirit, and a relentless appetite for learning are integral to my approach. Keen to connect and tackle new challenges together!
